verbose_text: In our study, biochemical assays of malondialdehyde (MDA), superoxide dismutase (SOD), catalase (CAT), glutathione (GSH) levels, histopathology and expression levels of vascular endothelial growth factor (VEGF) and B-cell lymphoma 2 (Bcl-2) were examined in testicular tissue by immunohistochemical methods.
